SSc-MIM — Dual License
======================

This repository is released under a dual licence:

* **Map content** — all CellDesigner SBML files (`curation/celldesigner/**`),
  annotation tables (`curation/annotations/**`), curated PubMed corpus
  (`curation/pubmed_corpus.bib`), MINERVA overlays (`minerva/overlays/**`),
  figures (`figures/**`), documentation (`docs/**`, `README.md`,
  `ROADMAP.md`, `CONTRIBUTING.md`), and manuscripts (`manuscript/**`) —
  is licensed under the **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
  Public License (CC-BY 4.0)**.

* **Code** — all scripts and notebooks under `analysis/**`, any code under
  `.github/workflows/**`, and any tooling code added later — is licensed
  under the **MIT License**.

By contributing to this repository you agree that your contributions
will be released under the same terms.

If in doubt about which licence applies to a given file, the file path
above is authoritative; otherwise contact the maintainers.

